@Node "V20" "NetCall_English.guide/V20"
@Next "V20a"
@Toc "HISTORY"

NetCall - Version 2.0
=====================

   @{b}*@{ub} First public release.


@EndNode

@Node "V20a" "NetCall_English.guide/V20a"
@Next "V20b"
@Prev "V20"
@Toc "HISTORY"

NetCall - Version 2.0a
======================

   @{b}*@{ub} English documents included.

   @{b}*@{ub} New config-variable: MAXRETRIES.

   @{b}*@{ub} Minor ALLACTIVE-bug fixed.

   @{b}*@{ub} New shell-argument: TERMREQS. Supports automatical operation.


@EndNode

@Node "V20b" "NetCall_English.guide/V20b"
@Next "V20c"
@Prev "V20a"
@Toc "HISTORY"

NetCall - Version 2.0b
======================

   @{b}*@{ub} New config-variable: CALL.

   @{b}*@{ub} Minor bug fixed: no text was displayed in the text-gadget on
     startup under  some conditions.

   @{b}*@{ub} New config-variable: BACKDROPWINDOW.

   @{b}*@{ub} New config-variable: STARTUPDELAY.

   @{b}*@{ub} Minor bug fixed: NetCall opened two requesters on exit (instead of
     exiting)  under some conditions.

   @{b}*@{ub} Minor bug fixed: font adaption problem of the text-gadget solved.

   @{b}*@{ub} #?.REQ-file editor ('request file') added.

   @{b}*@{ub} New config-variable: WINDOWFILEREQ.

   @{b}*@{ub} New config-variable: WINDOWFILEREQZOOM.

   @{b}*@{ub} New config-variable: AFTERSESSION.

   @{b}*@{ub} Now supports TrapDoor in resident mode, too.

   @{b}*@{ub} New config-variable: TRAPTELL.

   @{b}*@{ub} New shell-argument: TELL.

   @{b}*@{ub} New config-variable: SCREENTOFRONT.

   @{b}*@{ub} New config-variable: SUPRESSREQ.

   @{b}*@{ub} New config-variable: SAVELASTPOLLDATE.

   @{b}*@{ub} New menu-item: Rescan outbound.

   @{b}*@{ub} New menu-item: Add node entry.

   @{b}*@{ub} Expanded BOSS-config-variable.

   @{b}*@{ub} Changes in the OUTBOUND-directory will immediately become  visible
     in the listview-gadgets of NetCall (notify-function).

   @{b}*@{ub} All entries in the listview-gadget can now be selected with the
     function-keys, too.


@EndNode

@Node "V20c" "NetCall_English.guide/V20c"
@Prev "V20b"
@Toc "HISTORY"

NetCall - Version 2.0c
======================

   @{b}*@{ub} 'CONNECT'-requester in TELL-mode removed.

   @{b}*@{ub} The old config-parser had problems with spaces in the BOSS-entry
     ("BeforeSession" and "AfterSession") -> fixed.

   @{b}*@{ub} MAXRETRIES didn't work correctly -> fixed.

   @{b}*@{ub} New config-variable: ADDNODE.

   @{b}*@{ub} Toolbox: @{b}NetCall@{ub} features a window with user-defineable gadgets
     within. The functions of these gadgets can be defined by the user
     (start  programms/scripts, send ARexx-commands etc.). Use the
     COMMAND-variable to  configure the toolbox.

   @{b}*@{ub} New config-variable: WINDOWTOOLBOX.

   @{b}*@{ub} ARexx-interface (port: NETCALL).

   @{b}*@{ub} Installer-script will not overwrite the old NetCall.cfg now.

   @{b}*@{ub} If @{b}NetCall@{ub} gets started a second time, a requester will appear
     (to bring the old screen of @{b}NetCall@{ub} to the front).

   @{b}*@{ub} The list-view-gadget in the 'Select node...'-window ('Request
     file') uses  now 2-column output (looks nicer). (OS3.0 and above)

   @{b}*@{ub} Improved handling of very big fonts (GUI).

   @{b}*@{ub}     @{b}NetCall@{ub} now needs extacy.library >= V3.78.

   @{b}*@{ub} New config-variable: MAXRETRIESCOMMAND.

   @{b}*@{ub} New config-variable: REDIALDELAYENTRY.

   @{b}*@{ub}     @{i}NodeListUpdate@{ui}-script included in the archive.


@EndNode

